## Neon Postgres (Prisma)
#
# DATABASE_URL must be the **pooled** Neon URL for runtime queries:
# - include: ?pgbouncer=true&connect_timeout=15
#
# DIRECT_URL must be the **direct** Neon URL (no pooling) for migrations.
#
# Examples (replace with your real Neon values):
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST.neon.tech/DB?pgbouncer=true&connect_timeout=15&schema=public"
DIRECT_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST.neon.tech/DB?schema=public"